AUDIO: 'Dear Fellow Scholars, this is Two Minute&nbsp; Papers with Dr. Károly Zsolnai-Fehér. Well, the old way, called diffusion, was&nbsp; a shortcut. Imagine light hitting skin&nbsp;&nbsp; like a pebble in milky water. It just&nbsp; assumes a blurry circle will come out,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[04:38] [scene:talk]
