AUDIO: 'which is just a fast shortcut. But not reality. Now, instead, this new technique uses&nbsp; path tracing. Now that is a the real deal,&nbsp;&nbsp; it simulates the actual journey of&nbsp; individual light rays. It\'s like a&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[04:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'virtual game of pinball. Like a ball,&nbsp; each ray of light penetrates the skin,&nbsp;&nbsp; goes on a journey scattering inside&nbsp; the material until it finds its way&nbsp;&nbsp; out. The technique does this for millions&nbsp; of light rays to build up the final image.'

[05:09] [scene:talk]
